description: "A map of Java with mountains, jungles, animals and crops. Bathymetry (sea depth) is marked, including on an inset map of Batavia harbour. Illustrations include Batavia Castle, and a lion—representing Belgium—receiving tribute and enslaving locals."
title: "Insulae Iavae pars Occidentalis edente Hadriano Relando : Insulae Iavae pars Orientalis edente Hadriano Relando / t Amsterdam by Gerard van Keulen aan de Nieuwe brug met Privilegie ; J. Keyser fecit."
